The paper discusses the CL-SciSumm Shared Task 2018, which is a shared task on scientific document summarization in the computational linguistics (CL) domain. Therefore, cs.CL is the most likely sub-category. The task also involves information retrieval (IR) and machine learning (LG, AI, DL) techniques, which are relevant to the other sub-categories listed.
